Singer Bien Baraza has warmed hearts with a sweet message to his wife, Chiki Kuruka. In a competition that Sauti Sol's members are participating in, he nominated Chiki as 'the person who has impacted his life in the most extraordinary yet unexpected way'. "She has been the cornerstone of my music career, So loving, assuring, generous, patient and much more," he said. "She deserves the world and more. I pray for abundance and all the good things money can't buy. #Love with a difference, #Love more." Bien challenged fans to participate in the competition. Savara nominated all Sauti Sol members, Chimano his three siblings, while Polycarp nominated his son Sulwe, saying his mere existence had brought so much joy in his life. "He loves me without prejudice and judgement."